epresents the \"walk in newness of life\" that begins with faith and ends in glory. The image is hopeful and transcendent. Palette: deep indigo, starfield, volumetric blues, with a brilliant gold path.\nNegative: no text, no watermarks, no logos, no modern dress, no anachronisms, no captions, no UI elements, no faces.\n```\n",
