        "slide_deck_sidecar": "## Slide Deck Sidecar\n```markdown\n---\nbook: \"Acts\"\nchapter: \"14\"\nsection: \"9\"\nvisual_palette: sepia parchment, dust-light, ochre\n---\n\n# Acts 14:9 — The Apostolic Discernment of Saving Faith\nPaul's Spirit-enabled discernment of a lame man's gospel-born faith becomes the catalyst for his miraculous healing, demonstrating that the Word creates the faith required to receive God's power.\n\n*Slide deck: 7 sections, 7 total sub-slides, ≤5 bullets per slide.*\n",
        "slide_deck_sidecar_html": "<h2>Slide Deck Sidecar</h2>\n<h2>```markdown</h2>\n<p>book: \"Acts\"\nchapter: \"14\"\nsection: \"9\"\nvisual_palette: sepia parchment, dust-light, ochre</p>\n<hr>\n<h1>Acts 14:9 — The Apostolic Discernment of Saving Faith</h1>\n<p>Paul's Spirit-enabled discernment of a lame man's gospel-born faith becomes the catalyst for his miraculous healing, demonstrating that the Word creates the faith required to receive God's power.</p>\n<p><em>Slide deck: 7 sections, 7 total sub-slides, ≤5 bullets per slide.</em></p>",
