o watermarks, no logos, no modern dress, no anachronisms, no captions, no UI elements, no faces of named biblical figures except as symbolic representation.\n```\n```nano-banana-horizon\nAnchor: The Christo-telic Horizon — the Cross as the only true sacrifice.\nA powerful, minimalist cinematic still of a rough, empty wooden cross standing on a hill. The sky behind it is clearing after a storm, with rays of light breaking through dark clouds. At the base of the cross, a single, simple clay jar lies broken, its contents spilled out like a sacrifice. This image represents the final, sufficient sacrifice of Christ that renders all other sacrifices obsolete. High-contrast chiaroscuro, ember-and-shadow palette.\nNegative: no text, no watermarks, no logos, no modern dress, no anachronisms, no captions, no UI elements, no faces of named biblical figures except as symbolic representation.\n```\n",
