lements, no faces of named biblical figures except as symbolic representation.\n```\n```nano-banana-horizon\nAnchor: Christo-telic Horizon — In Christ, all things hold together (Col 1:17).\nA breathtaking, symbolic cosmic image. The camera looks down on the Earth from space, but instead of continents, the planet's surface is a vibrant, living tapestry of agricultural fields in every season—green shoots, golden wheat, fallow earth. Swirling cloud patterns deliver rain. Holding the entire globe, rendered as a transparent sphere, is the faint, star-like silhouette of a cross, signifying Christ as the sustainer of all life. Palette: deep indigo, starfield, volumetric blues, earth tones.\nNegative: no text, no watermarks, no logos, no modern dress, no anachronisms, no captions, no UI elements, no faces of named biblical figures except as symbolic representation.\n```\n",
