his passage points to Christ by showing that the life of a disciple is a re-enactment of the Master's life. To follow Christ is to walk the path He walked, which was the way of the cross leading to the crown (1 Pet 2:21). Our suffering is a participation in His (Phil 3:10).</li>\n</ul>",
