f these cities in the Roman provincial system, providing the historical backdrop for Luke's accurate geography.</li>\n<li><strong>Christ-Centered Hermeneutic Verification:</strong> This passage points to Christ by showing the faithful execution of His Great Commission. The apostles are not acting on their own initiative but as ambassadors for the risen King, proclaiming \"the word\" about Him. Their work is a direct consequence of Christ's finished work and His command to make disciples of all nations.</li>\n</ul>",
