        "slide_deck_sidecar": "## Slide Deck Sidecar\n```markdown\n---\nbook: \"Acts\"\nchapter: \"14\"\nsection: \"26\"\nvisual_palette: warm amber, low-key key-light, gold-hour skin tones\n---\n\n# Acts 14:26 — The Missionary Report: Grace Entrusted, Grace Fulfilled\nThis single verse encapsulates the entire theology of Christian mission: a divine entrustment to God's grace, requiring faithful completion and accountable reporting back to the sending church.\n\n*Slide deck: 7 sections, 7 total sub-slides, ≤5 bullets per slide.*\n",
